Na žalost, neću se takmičiti ove godine u Njujorku. Želim svim igračima dobar turnir. Hvala mom #NoleFam-u za svu ljubav, podršku i ohrabrenje. Nastavljam da čuvam formu i optimizam i radujem se novim takmičenjima. Vidimo se uskoro! 🙏🏼❤️👋🏼

Sadly, I will not be able to travel to NY this time for US Open. Thank you #NoleFam for your messages of love and support. ❤️ Good luck to my fellow players! I’ll keep in good shape and positive spirit and wait for an opportunity to compete again. 💪🏼 See you soon tennis world! 👋🏼
Ja nastavljam da se pripremam i treniram kao da ću se takmičiti dok iščekujem odgovor da li postoji bilo kakva mogućnost da putujem u Ameriku. Hvala vam i držite mi palčeve!🤞🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼❤️
Velika mi je čast što toliko ljudi podržava moju karijeru i želi da me vidi ponovo na terenima širom sveta.

Želim samo da iskoristim priliku da podelim sa vama koliko mi znači vaša podrška i ljubav koju mi šaljete ovih dana. 

Nisam je očekivao u tolikom broju i zato je moja zahvalnost i veća!  Stvarno od srca veliko HVALA. 🙏🏼❤️
I am preparing as if I will be allowed to compete, while I await to hear if there is any room for me to travel to US. Fingers crossed! 🤞🏼💪🏼https://t.co/cIDfdPtZ5t
It feels special that people connect with my tennis career in such a loving and supportive way and wish for me to continue to compete.

I just wanted to take a moment and say to all of you how grateful I am to see so many messages of support and love from all around the world these days. 🙏🏼

I wasn’t expecting it, and that’s why it feels so mindblowing. Just wanted to say THANK YOU. 🙏🏼❤️

I’m pleased and grateful that the Judge overturned my visa cancellation. Despite all that has happened,I want to stay and try to compete @AustralianOpen

Prijalo mi je da budem sa svojom porodicom i dragim ljudima, odmorio sam se od veoma duge i uspešne sezone 2021. Sada krećem u Australiju jer sam dobio izuzeće i spreman sam da živim i dišem tenis narednih par nedelja takmičenja. Hvala svima na podršci! Idemooooo ‘22 💪🏼
Srećna svima Nova godina! Želim vam mnogo zdravlja, ljubavi, radosti i sreće. Da vidite, dišete i mislite ljubav i da negujete poštovanje prema svakoj osobi i živom biću na ovoj divnoj planeti. ❤️🙏🏼

Happy New Year! Wishing you all health, love & joy in every moment & may you feel love & respect towards all beings on this wonderful planet.

Činjenica da sam imao jak tim pravilo je veliku razliku u mojoj karijeri i želim da takvo okruženje pružim svim talentima u akademiji. Raiffeisen je važan partner koji je prepoznao našu misiju i zajedno ćemo raditi na razvoju i unapređenju tenisa.

Počastvovan sam što sam postao brand ambasador i partner Raiffeisen banke u projektu Teniske akademije "Novak Djoković" koji mi je veoma važan. Sada ćemo još snažnije podržati mlade tenisere u nastojanju da postanu šampioni kako na terenu, tako i van njega. 😃🎾🙏🏼🙌🏼

Having a strong team along my side has made a huge difference for my career. Therefore, I wish to offer such environment to the future generation of players in my academy. @RBI_Presse is an important partner in this effort and together we will work towards helping tennis grow.

I’m honored to become a brand ambassador for @RBI_Presse and partner with them on a very important project for me – my academy in Belgrade. They will help me to support young tennis players in their efforts to become champions both on and off the court. 😃🎾🙏🏼🙌🏼🙌🏼 https://t.co/RCnSD9N76Q
